data.description: Welcome home. That's what you'll say to this one. This beautiful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is now for sale in a quiet and friendly neighborhood. With the open layout this property offers plenty of room for comfortable living. When you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting open living area perfect for relaxing or entertaining. Adjacent to the living area is a sunroom, providing abundance of natural light that can serve as an office, playroom, or additional sitting area. The kitchen features plenty of counter space making meal preparation a breeze. You can enjoy your meals in the adjacent breakfast area. Outside you'll find a fenced yard that offers privacy and security, making it the perfect space for the kids, pets or outdoor activities. You'll also find a storage building that provides extra room for all the belongings. This property is conveniently located in the heart of Pleasant Grove with easy access to the local amenities such as shopping, restaurants, and parks. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your next home. Contact me today to schedule your private showing and experience the comfort and convenience the property has to offer.
